    "description": "<strong> The Dawn is Inevitable</strong> is an interactive novel from a small indie studio <strong>Last Spring</strong>, known for the text adventure <strong>Forbidden Valley</strong>.<br><br><strong> Unfortunately, English localization is not available at the moment, but we are trying to find means to release it as soon as possible. Thank you for your attention!</strong><br><br>The mysterious stranger named <strong>Victor</strong> is forced to lie low in a place called <strong>Rassvet</strong>. This is a village hidden in the Chazytchir Valley beyond the ridges of the <strong>Sayan Mountains</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144770/extras/138e23508fcd499f07fca544c16308ed.poster.avif?t=1664799916\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144770/extras/138e23508fcd499f07fca544c16308ed.webm?t=1664799916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144770/extras/138e23508fcd499f07fca544c16308ed.mp4?t=1664799916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>During the long Siberian winter, Rassvet is almost completely <strong>isolated</strong> from the outside world. During this period, it is incredibly <strong>hard to get in</strong>... but even <strong>harder to get out of there</strong>.<br><br>Of course, in a place like this, things couldn't be as easy as Victor had hoped. And he had no idea what trials would fall to his lot when he decided to go to the Rassvet.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144770/extras/f7dcbe32b9461d869952fd0b545461e5.poster.avif?t=1664799916\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor